Hi there! And thank you for downloading my map. I appreciate the support and hope you enjoy it! All 
materials included in this file were made from scratch by me, Donnie Lewis, aka PBX. The following 
programs were used:

Blender: www.blender.org
Paint.NET: www.getpaint.net 


Map was made with the valve Hammer Editor.
Materials were zipped into the bsp using the BSPZIP tool.



*****INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS:*****

This map has custom materials but they are integrated into the map's bsp file, Just drag the bsp into
your maps folder and youre good!

This is my best map so far, I put it on my server, changed the map to this one, and we played it, at least 8 times, people loved it, I had fun, and it's just a great map. There is more then 1 way to get to the other side: Two main doors, two side obstacles, and a great bridge. It's a GunGame map, but I'm making it also for normal game play. I'll add buy zones, and a bomb site, hostages were on my mind, but, the map is a bit too small for that, so I'm sticking with the two. My name in-game is »P-T« мικε, so I added a rotating 'MIKE', in the middle. Problem is, that it rotates on the Y axis, I want it to rotate horizontally, can you tell me how to? It has a rotating sound. The doors are shoot activated, touch activated, and use activated. Once again, more then one way to get across to enemy territory. Tell me what you think about it.

<fieldset>This is going to be my latest map designed for Counter-Strike: Source GunGame mod. Its currently undergoing the making of its life time. I've put about 10-15 hours into this so far, and its not even 1/4 of the way there. I'm going to make a door that goes to the mapper credits currently "Pyro-Teknix" and underdevelopment is "Green Mike". In the credits room there will be door buttons and light switches outside, and in, on both sides. There will be music which will be but in which I will establish soon. This map is me trying to be as various and broad as possible with the realistic/cartoon/fun/random map, just a general GunGame/DeathMatch map. Enjoy in a few, the estimated release date will be around Januray 8th-15th, 2008.</fieldset>

My first and probably last Gun Game map ever.

The map is created for an average gungame server. It has 96 T and 96 CT spawns.
It is fully symmetrical.

When you die, your dead body will be sucked into space.

There is also a secret. There are two invisible buttons. Can you find them?
If you press them all, there will be a 1/5th chance the secret will be activated. You cannot be more camouflaged if you manage to activate the secret properly.

Thanks to Shini for the skybox and Defekt for the textures.
And thanks to Pendulum Studio for all the feedback.

/Helix

Warning: There is a chance of low fps in the middle of the map. Good graphic card computers will have less trouble with this. I did not have a bad fps drop, just a small one.

Warning 2: I did not put a game_player_equip entity in it, so if you start without the mod you will get a knife and your secondary gun. (glock/usp). I don't know if this will conflict with the GG mod.

My new map based off a map from the game Turok Rage Wars for the N64. The map itself isn't exactly like the map from the origonal game, but I got some ideas from it. I was originally trying to make an exact replica of the map from the N64 game, but when I decided that I couldn't do that successfully, i took what I had already made and made a few creative changes to it and finished it up. And this is the finished version of the map. It does have a few slight errors, but nothing that will effect the gameplay at all. I had to make a huge box around the map itself so make sure that I wouldn't get any leaks since all the walls in the main map are only 5 units thick. I did also include buy zones for people who want to play regular gameplay.

But, I hope you enjoy the map!
